      propertyPath: 'dialog.Array.data[2]'
      value: "What do you mean I could have teleported you to the Pizza anytime?
        \nYou don't know what you're talking about!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1708576647234818529, guid: 6bcbd75a4bd4dba45802087238127d31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialog.Array.data[3]'
      value: I thought about it and maybe it's time I stop carrying around this old
        pizza and finally eat it.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1708576647234818529, guid: 6bcbd75a4bd4dba45802087238127d31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialog.Array.data[4]'
