      propertyPath: 'dialog.Array.data[0]'
      value: Brave Adventurer, I am in depserate need of your help!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1708576647234818529, guid: 6bcbd75a4bd4dba45802087238127d31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialog.Array.data[1]'
      value: "My evil roomate Lenny has stolen my most prized posession: \na Pizza
        my mother gave to me when I was going through a rough time last year. \nWill
        you please help me get it back?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1708576647234818529, guid: 6bcbd75a4bd4dba45802087238127d31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialog.Array.data[2]'
      value: "He has the location written in his lab notes, \nbut you'll need the
        two keys to enter our \nhigh-security lab to get to the notes."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1708576647234818529, guid: 6bcbd75a4bd4dba45802087238127d31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialog.Array.data[3]'
      value: ...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1708576647234818529, guid: 6bcbd75a4bd4dba45802087238127d31, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialog.Array.data[4]'
      value: "Why can't I get it? I'm... uh... busy guarding this door. \nIt's a
        lot of hard work!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1708576647234818529, guid: 6bcbd75a4bd4dba45802087238127d31, type: 3}
